# DTS Product Philosophy (产品理念规则)

Scope: all DTS projects under `/opt/prod/dts/rdc`

## Core Identity

DTS is an AI-driven Enterprise Decision Operating System.
Core formula: Ontology (data foundation) + Intent (understanding) + Agent (execution).
Not a data platform. Not a BI tool. Not a chatbot wrapper.

## Know-how as Asset

- The product's ultimate value is turning expert tacit knowledge into executable capability packs.
- One expert's experience × AI extraction × system scale = 500x output.
- AI is an amplifier, not an inventor. It cannot create industry experience from nothing.
- The platform must enable domain experts to create capability packs through natural conversation with AI, NOT through coding.

## AI Positioning

- AI is the primary execution engine, not an optional enhancement.
- Default path: AI-driven. Fallback path: manual operation (Law 1).
- AI does NOT replace experts. AI maximizes expert value.
- AI Agent must be the main actor; Java services are tools the Agent calls.
- The system must support AI-to-AI communication (Agent Protocol) for future cross-organization collaboration.

## Competitive Moat

- Industry Know-how accumulation: each customer deepens the knowledge flywheel.
- Knowledge lock-in: switching away means losing core competitive advantage, not just data.
- Five Iron Laws: the trust foundation that makes customers willing to let AI drive decisions.
- Offline deployment + data sovereignty: unmatched in government/defense/critical infrastructure.

## Market Strategy Alignment

- 5-day Proof of Value (POV): real customer data, real results, then sign.
- Capability Before Interface (Law 5): never demo features that don't work end-to-end.
- Investment protection: DTS sits on top of existing systems (ERP/MES/CRM), does not replace them.
- Four revenue layers: platform fee + capability pack subscription + knowledge output sharing + professional services.

## Multi-modal Future (P2)

- Architecture must accommodate future multi-modal inputs (voice, vision, video).
- dts-perception service is reserved for this purpose.
- dts-intent-engine receives structured Intents, NOT raw text — enabling new modalities without downstream changes.
